data.title: Folk musician
data.meta_description: David Fisher is a musician based in Birmingham. Find out about his music, gigs and latest releases here
data.text:
David Fisher's second album, Busking Beyond Borders, is now out. Find out more here

'Busking Beyond Borders adroitly captures the beauty, magic and unpredictable thrill of life on the road'

The Fix Magazine

'David's busking has resulted in a powerful, distinctive voice... ('Busking Beyond Borders') will delight the listener, particularly if accompanied by a reading of David's book'

Folk Monthly

'David's voice is strong with an attractive, raw power... hints of the styles of Gordon Lightfoot and Richard Thompson'

Unicorn Magazine

'Really raw, fresh sound... If you like live music you'll really enjoy it'

Marie Crichton, BBC Shropshire

'Fisher has a talent for songwriting... He made a big impression'

FolkAll

'There's a cosy, warm feeling that washes over you when you listen to any music by David Fisher... Ten beautiful tracks'

Lucy Onions Music
